tps://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2024-Pivot-Shuttle-AM-steep-climb.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Frame color options for all models are Blue Neptune or Mojave Willow Green. The Shuttle AM Team and Pro models are available at Pivot dealers as of today, while the Ride model is coming soon.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.pivotcycles.com/en/\">pivotcycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pivot-bosch-powered-2024-shuttle-am-emtb/\">Pivot Launches the Bosch-Powered 2024 Shuttle AM eMTB</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Steve Fisher","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"90beb20501399d41d1d765fc832b1a0f5012ad19421612648120bb0a0c399574","category":"Cycling"}